{"tha-ap419:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap419:0.2":"Bhaddalivagga ","tha-ap419:0.3":"Ucchangapupphiyattheraapadana ","tha-ap419:1.1":"“Nagare bandhumatiya, ","tha-ap419:1.2":"ahosim maliko tada; ","tha-ap419:1.3":"Ucchangam purayitvana, ","tha-ap419:1.4":"agamam antarapanam. ","tha-ap419:2.1":"Bhagava tamhi samaye, ","tha-ap419:2.2":"bhikkhusanghapurakkhato; ","tha-ap419:2.3":"Mahata anubhavena, ","tha-ap419:2.4":"niyyati lokanayako. ","tha-ap419:3.1":"Disvana lokapajjotam, ","tha-ap419:3.2":"vipassim lokataranam; ","tha-ap419:3.3":"Puppham paggayha ucchanga, ","tha-ap419:3.4":"buddhasettham apujayim. ","tha-ap419:4.1":"Ekanavutito kappe, ","tha-ap419:4.2":"yam pupphamabhipujayim; ","tha-ap419:4.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap419:4.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap419:5.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap419:5.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap419:5.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap419:6.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap419:6.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap419:6.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap419:7.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap419:7.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap419:7.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap419:8.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma ucchangapupphiyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap419:9.1":"Ucchangapupphiyattherassapadanam sattamam. "}